{"lemma":"أُسَرُ","slug":"أُسَرُ","root":"#.س.ر","root_slug":"_-س-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-س-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أُسَرُ","root":"أسر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n743","n747","n748","n749","n19439"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8F%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"family"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of سَرِير (sarīr)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔus.ra/","/ʔa.sir.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n743","headword_ar":"اسّر","root":"Asr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tied, tight, fast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firmly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(So accord. to Golius; but for this he names no authority.)]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n747","headword_ar":"اَسْرٌ","root":"Asr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isaArN","text_ar":"اـِسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (S.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA Al$~aYo'u laka biA^asorihi","text_ar":"هٰذَا الشَّىْءُ لَكَ بِاَسْرِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This thing is for thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is thine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with its thong of untanned hide"},{"kind":"text","text":"[wherewith it is bound]; meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altogether;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"birum~atihi","text_ar":"بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu*ohu biA^asorihi","text_ar":"خُذْهُ بِاَسْرِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Take thou it all,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altogether."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a Alqawomu biA^asorihimo","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ القَوْمُ بِاَسْرِهِمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people came altogether."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Bekr.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strength of make,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"form."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) [Accord. to the copies of the K in my hands, it also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strength of natural disposition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlxuluq","text_ar":"وَالخُلُق"},{"kind":"text","text":", in those copies,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":58},{"kind":"text","text":"we should read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlxaloqu","text_ar":"وَالخَلْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with other lexicons, as is implied in the TA: see 1.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN $adiydN A^asorK Alxaloqi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ شَدِيدٌ اَسْرٍ الخَلْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is of strong, firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact, make,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"form."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adadonaA A^asorahumo","text_ar":"شَدَدْنَا اَسْرَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [lxxvi. 28], means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have strengthened their make,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"form:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their joints:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their two sphincters which serve as repressers of the urine and feces"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSar~ataYi Albawoli wa AlgaAy^iTi","text_ar":"مَصَرَّتَىِ البَوْلِ وَ الغَايِطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), which contract when the excrement has passed forth; or the meaning is, that these two things do not become relaxed before one desires. (IAar, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n748","headword_ar":"اُسْرٌ","root":"Asr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, IKtt, A,) a subst., (M, IKtt,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usurN","text_ar":"اُسُرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Lb,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Suppression of the urine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, &c.:) suppression of the feces is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuSorN","text_ar":"حُصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dribbling of the urine, with a cutting pain in the bladder, and pangs like those of a female in the time of parturition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu AlA^asoru","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ الاَسْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Suppression of urine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaAlahu A@ll~`hu A^usorAF","text_ar":"اَنَالَهُ ا@للّٰهُ اُسْراً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God give him a suppression of urine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: a form of imprecation. (A.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euwdu A^usorK","text_ar":"عُودُ اُسْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, M, A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwdN A^usorN","text_ar":"عُودٌ اُسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euwdu AlA^usori","text_ar":"عُودُ الاُسْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Expositions of the Fs) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euwdu yusori","text_ar":"عُودُ يُسْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, K,) or this is a corruption, (K,) or a vulgar mistake, (A,) and should not be said, (Fr, S, A,) unless meant to be used as ominous of good, (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of wood, which is put upon the belly of a man affected by a suppression of his urine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and which cures him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","IKtt","A","Lb","IAar","K","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n749","headword_ar":"اُسُرٌ","root":"Asr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usorN","text_ar":"اُسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19439","headword_ar":"اَسَرُّ","root":"sr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An adventive; one abiding among a people to whom he is not related;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daxiylN","text_ar":"دَخِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) Lebeed says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wajad~iY faArisu Alr~aEo$aA='i minohumo\n                      \n                     \n                        ray^iysN laA A^asar~u walaA saniydu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And my grandfather, the rider of Er-Raashà,"},{"kind":"text","text":"was"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of them; a chief, not an adventive, nor of suspected origin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A2-  Also a camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a gall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sore, in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kirokirap","text_ar":"كِرْكِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"callous projection upon the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a pain therein, arising from a gall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sore:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1340},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having sores in the hinder part thereof, nearly penetrating into his inside, but not mortal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the disorder termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~N","text_ar":"ضَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is a tumour in the breast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~aA='u","text_ar":"سَرَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sararN","text_ar":"سَرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanodN A^asar~u","text_ar":"زَنْدٌ اَسَرُّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"znd","text_ar":"زند"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of stick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wood, for producing fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has become hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by wear"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AHn, S, M, K. [See 1, near the end of the paragraph.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qanaApN sar~aA='u","text_ar":"قَنَاةٌ سَرَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hollow spearshaft."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","M"]}]}}